title: Circuit Breaker
description: Maintenance activities for Circuit Breaker in HV SWGR system

body.raw:
# Circuit Breaker

## Activities

1. Contact Resist.
2. Timing Open-Close
3. Ins. Resist.
4. Coil Pickup
5. SF6 Gas Press.-Purity
6. Vacuum Integrity
7. Mech. Operation
